short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Writefull is automated proofreading for academic writing. This version of Writefull provides support for Overleaf.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
As Overleaf has integrated Writefull, this extension will soon become inactive. Please enable Writefull from within Overleaf instead. Go to your Overleaf Account Settings page, scroll down to ‘Integrations’, and enable Writefull from there! 

Writefull provides support for Overleaf, giving language suggestions tailored to research writing, features to generate LaTeX code, and options to paraphrase, summarize, and more.
